    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the CFD hemolysis prediction model is accepted at MRL 2 for Class II CPB device evaluation. Seven of thirteen factors were formally assessed; all assessed factors met or exceeded their required credibility levels. Remaining factors were determined not-assessed or not-applicable at MRL 2 given medium model influence. Output comparison results (max deviation 9.4%) satisfy the ±15% acceptance criterion. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions per the stated COU.",
